== 个人生活 ==
哈德森在2008年赛季结束后和凯伊莎·卡尔（{{lang-en|Keisa Carr}}）结婚。他们拥有一个女儿和一个儿子<ref>{{cite web | url = http://mlb.mlb.com/team/player.jsp?player_id=407861 | title = Orlando Hudson: Stats, Bio, Photos, Highlights | access-date = 2009-11-30 | archive-date = 2015-02-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150214181702/http://mlb.mlb.com/team/player.jsp?player_id=407861 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

哈德森成立一个名叫C.A.T.C.H.的基金会，用于帮助患有[[自闭症|自闭症]]的儿童。

